                </div>
                <div class="team-card">
                    <div class="team-card-inner">
                        <div class="team-photo">
                            <div class="photo-placeholder" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);">
                                <span class="initials">JS</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="photo-overlay">
                                <div class="social-links">
                                    <a href="#" class="social-icon" aria-label="LinkedIn">
                                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                            <path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                                            <rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                                            <circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                                        </svg>
                                    </a>
                                    <a href="#" class="social-icon" aria-label="Email">
                                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                            <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                                            <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                                        </svg>
                                    </a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="team-content">
                            <h3 class="team-name">John Smith</h3>
                            <p class="team-role">Chief Technology Officer</p>
                            <p class="team-bio">AI researcher from MIT, pioneering medical AI applications.</p>
                            <div class="team-stats">
                                <div class="stat-item">
                                    <span class="stat-value">15+</span>
                                    <span class="stat-label">Years</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="stat-item">
                                    <span class="stat-value">50+</span>
                                    <span class="stat-label">Patents</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="team-card">
                    <div class="team-card-inner">
                        <div class="team-photo">
                            <div class="photo-placeholder" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4facfe 0%, #00f2fe 100%);">
                                <span class="initials">SC</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="photo-overlay">
                                <div class="social-links">
                                    <a href="#" class="social-icon" aria-label="LinkedIn">
                                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                            <path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                                            <rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                                            <circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                                        </svg>
                                    </a>
                                    <a href="#" class="social-icon" aria-label="Email">
                                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                            <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                                            <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                                        </svg>
                                    </a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="team-content">
                            <h3 class="team-name">Dr. Sarah Chen</h3>
                            <p class="team-role">Head of Clinical Operations</p>
                            <p class="team-bio">Stanford Medicine graduate, expert in telemedicine and patient care.</p>
                            <div class="team-stats">
                                <div class="stat-item">
                                    <span class="stat-value">12+</span>
                                    <span class="stat-label">Years</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="stat-item">
                                    <span class="stat-value">10K+</span>
                                    <span class="stat-label">Patients</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="team-card">
                    <div class="team-card-inner">
                        <div class="team-photo">
                            <div class="photo-placeholder" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fa709a 0%, #fee140 100%);">
                                <span class="initials">MJ</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="photo-overlay">
                                <div class="social-links">
                                    <a href="#" class="social-icon" aria-label="LinkedIn">
                                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                            <path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                                            <rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                                            <circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                                        </svg>
                                    </a>
                                    <a href="#" class="social-icon" aria-label="Email">
                                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                            <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                                            <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                                        </svg>
                                    </a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="team-content">
                            <h3 class="team-name">Michael Johnson</h3>
                            <p class="team-role">Chief Data Officer</p>
                            <p class="team-bio">Former Google AI lead, specializing in healthcare data analytics and privacy.</p>
                            <div class="team-stats">
                                <div class="stat-item">
                                    <span class="stat-value">18+</span>
                                    <span class="stat-label">Years</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="stat-item">
                                    <span class="stat-value">100M+</span>
